social_posts.post_text: Before the holiday madness begins I just wanna say that this recent #Miami trip was beyond productive. The things set in motion are gonna be life changing and we couldn’t be more grateful to everyone that helped us while we were out there. Big Thank you to the following people: Our in house team @djdennisdamenace @cookie_nayira @natasha_melina @gisxo @its_marialuna @budaink @basiliosilvaphoto @prmike214 , to my brother #Maffio you’re genuine love and humility is something to aspire for. Your stage presence is magic and we’re truly blessed to have you part of this. To the whole #VibraUrbana staff for your continued support and always including us in such historical events. To our @playnskillz family, the chemistry in studio was so special. We’re incredibly excited for 2023. I can’t wait for the world to hear what was created! To our partners @jackdaniels_us for always going above and beyond 💪🏼🙏🏼 To #CentroWynwood for your warm hospitality. All the Photographers and videographers.for the great images and content And to the amazing dancers for your dedication and hard work. Tags will be in pics and in comments. Wishing everyone a safe and happy holidays. 🙏🏼🙏🏼🙏🏼

Do not confuse ACTIVITY with PRODUCTIVITY. Stay focused and disciplined. The results will come. Blessings to all in the #NewYear 🙏🏼

#TBT This was the winter of #1985 A few of my friends had sheepskin coats. I wanted one so badly but my father instead bought me an imitation one. I was not happy about that but when he explained why I understood. This was the height of the #CrackEpidemic and he didn’t want me getting killed over a coat. Back then people were losing their lives for a pair of sneakers. It took awhile but my 10 year old mind understood. #SunsetPark #Brooklyn #SheepskinCoat #HipHop50

social_posts.post_text: What a great experience it was to catch up with my friend Mark @loughneyart and see the #MarkingTime exhibit @schomburgcenter Who would’ve thought that some sketches in the day room prison in #SCIDallas would’ve sparked such an impactful movement. Thank you @nifleetwood for putting together such an amazing book and for continuing to shed light on #massincarceration
Although they weren’t always the best circumstances, I’m glad I got to see my boys grow up. #LoveMySons #TBT FYI #RibbonInTheSky is one of my favorite songs 🙏🏼 #StevieWonder #ThrowBackThursday
